11 A BILL
12 TO BE ENTITLED
13 AN ACT
14
15 Relating to motor vehicle registration; to amend
16 Sections 32-6-271 and 32-6-280, Code of Alabama 1975, to
17 increase the fees for volunteer and professional firefighter
18 distinctive motor vehicle license plates and to provide for
19 the distribution of the fees collected.
20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
21 Section 1. Sections 32-6-271 and 32-6-280, Code of
22 Alabama 1975, are amended to read as follows:
23 "§32-6-271
24 (a) A firefighter, upon application and subject to this
25 division, may be issued a distinctive motor vehicle license
26 plate as identification as a firefighter. In addition to the
27 proper numbers, words, and insignias used on the standard
28 license plate issued for motor vehicles, the distinctive
